name: Niobium Modular Web Browser
tagline: A browser that adapts to you
body:
#Niobium Web Browser

> Concept

A modular web-browser

## Dev

```
$ npm install
```

### Run

```
$ npm start
```

### Build

```
$ npm run build
```

Builds the app for OS X, Linux, and Windows, using [electron-packager](https://github.com/maxogden/electron-packager).
